I have no intent of fully cross-dressing even. I am comfortable with my male identity and sexuality. But I've always been fascinated by bras regardless back into my teens (I'm pushing 40 now), and about 6 weeks ago I decided to buy one. One turned into... more than one. Now, as long as I'm home alone and not going anywhere, I'm wearing a bra.

And honestly? Since I did some research and measured myself and made sure I got a fitting one, I'm seeing... benefits? Like I'm noticing/correcting my own posture more (I slouch a lot) since I'm actually physically supported?

Not sure if this goes anywhere or is a throwaway. It might die in usersub. But I wanted to vent it somewhere, anonymously, that I'm a straight, cis man who's decided - at lest for now - to wear a bra on the regular.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/8Rxfrs1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[pinballprogrock]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>200,000 subscribers *so far*</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/X8Zgmbk</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AsTFmip.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AfwHZ1J.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/R7ejtY4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wWirQmA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2gSuX8D.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.npr.org/2024/10/28/nx-s1-5168416/washington-post-bezos-endorsement-president-cancellations-resignations</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/X8Zgmbk</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BeetBoxer]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fuuuuuuuuuucccckkk</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Q3U7xFs</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fXbAqg2.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Q3U7xFs</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DOcelot]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Do we tell him?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DSW7bbO</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BMD4YTB.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DSW7bbO</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Othagovna]]></dc:creator></i